Title: Supply Only the Finest Goons
Description:
These "attendants" of my father's attacked us the moment we arrived!

These are certainly not the kindly servants I had as a child. These are hired killers!

If my father is planning what I think he's planning... we can't let them do this. They will kill everyone in their way.

<Cecilia winces.>

If it's kill or be killed...
ObjectivesText: Slay 16 Clessington Attendants in the Defias Hideout in Moonbrook.
